    for the Second Year: Games Development (Thematic Project)\n\nStudents were paired
    into allocated groups to create a functional project based on a topic assigned
    by the course-lead. This Unity Project shows the current completed group task
    of the assesment in allign with University regulations. \n\nThe project was created
    by the use of \"Unity, IDE's, Discord for communication and Trello for the planning
    and diary of the project.\n \n\r"
